Program: The Why Factor
Title: Why Football is the World’s Game
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cswrk2
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 25 Jun 2018
Why has football becomes the world’s favourite team sport? Aasmah Mir asks why “soccer” has developed such a huge following. As the FIFA World Cup kicks off in Russia, Aasmah talks to players and fans across the world about the game’s accessibility, simplicity and unpredictability. (Image: Children playing football on beach, Credit: Shutterstock) Show less